high_descs: Turn around, walk across the space between sofa and coffee table
Grab the plate on the table
Turn right, walk to the black table, turn right, and turn left, walk to the window, turn right, facing the dining table
Put the plate down on the table behind the bowl
Grab the tissue box on the right
Put it in the plate on the side
anns.task_desc: Move the plate from the coffee table to the dining table, put the tissue box in the plate

high_descs: Turn left and move to the couch, turn left again and move to the chair, turn right and move to the center of the coffee table, turn left to face the coffee table.
Pick up the dish on the coffee table.

Turn right and move past the couch, turn right and move to the wooden floor, turn left before the kitchen table, move forward all the way to the wall, turn right and move to the middle of the kitchen table, turn right and move to the table.
Place the plate on the center of the kitchen table to the left of the bowl.
Pick up the box of tissue on the right.
Place the box of tissue on its end on the plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a box of tissue on its end on the plate on the kitchen table.

high_descs: Cross the room and go to the couch
Get the plate off the coffee table
Turn around, cross the room, and take the plate to the kitchen table behind you
Set the plate down on the kitchen table
Get a box of tissues off the table
Set the box of tissues on the plate with the tissues facing your left
anns.task_desc: Get a plate from the coffee table
